Chili Cheese Burger

25 min
$12.99
750 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

glutendairy

Dietary Tags:

high-proteincomfort-food

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

burgerAmericaneasy

Description

A juicy burger topped with spicy chili and melted cheese for a satisfying meal.

Ingredients

  • ground beef: 1 lb
  • burger buns: 4
  • chili (canned or homemade): 2 cups
  • cheddar cheese (shredded): 1 cup
  • onion (diced): 1
  • pickles: to taste
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • garlic powder: 1 tsp
  • smoked paprika: 1 tsp
